<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ش د هـ:</span> <span class="c2">(شُدِهَ)</span> الرَّجُلُ <span class="c2">(شَدْهًا)</span> فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(مَشْدُوهٌ)</span> دُهِشَ وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الشَّدَهُ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الشُّدْهُ)</span> كَالْبَخَلِ وَالْبُخْلِ.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ أَبُو زَيْدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(شُدِهَ)</span> الرَّجُلُ شُغِلَ لَا غَيْرُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>